    "about": {
      "type": "about",
      "settings": {
        "badge_text": "Est. 2010",
        "eyebrow": "Meet Nazly",
        "heading": "Design with",
        "heading_accent": "soul & intention",
        "body": "<p>I'm Nazly — wife, mother of three, and someone who has spent most of her life quietly obsessed with beautiful rooms.</p><p>What started as a genuine love of chinoiserie, antiques and the kind of interiors you want to live inside rather than just admire, eventually became something more. When my children headed off to school and I finally had a few hours to myself, I decided to stop collecting inspiration and start making things.</p><p>Today, Nazly Habib Design is a small studio making handcrafted rattan, wicker and upholstered furniture — bespoke pieces built around your home, your taste and your life. Every piece is made to order, which means it was made for you.</p><p><em>I still can't believe this is my job.</em></p>",
        "signature": "— Nazly Habib"
      }
    },
